    ♪ Remember when
    we waltzed in the rain ♪

53:48.259 --> 53:52.995
      ♪ You know
      I am nobody's girl ♪

53:55.333 --> 54:02.104
  ♪ I just wasn't made
  for no diamonds or pearls ♪

54:02.106 --> 54:06.842
